<p><strong>4. What is the Target Audience for the Book?</strong></p>
<p>Stephen Pople's Physics Book is primarily aimed at high school and undergraduate students studying physics. It is also a valuable resource for teachers, researchers, and anyone interested in gaining a deeper understanding of physics.</p>
